  "text": "Experimental data are acquired using a micro-fabricated thermal micro-device associated to zeolite material. Zeolites are used as a selective layers as in other works in literature ( [CITATION_1] ). Zeolites are micro/nanoporous materials that reveal great chemical, size and shape selectivity enabling detection and differentiation between different gases and vapors.",
